{"tid":1976530,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：陳振聲鬧得好","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T04:34:46.000Z","uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f682f9ca1c4940b81d759f91d41f1dddd0467f04","tid":1976530,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"陳雲：新加坡貿易部長罵得好。香港人不只是低能和丟臉，而是愚昧、賤格、卑劣。我昨日大罵香港人之後，新加坡人壯了膽，夠膽罵香港人了。<br />\n//陳振聲認為，若新加坡學香港，一人一日一口罩，每日就要五百萬口罩；但疫情可能持續數月，這樣的需求根本無法滿足，所以新加坡必須有策略地使用口罩，分優次保證口罩的供應，首先是醫護人員，其次是的士司機、巴士司機或其他前線服務人員。他承認，不全民戴口罩或許是一場賭博，但可以確保有足夠的儲備。<br />\n陳振聲又提到香港目前出現的市民搶購糧食及廁紙的現象，認為是「monkey see monkey do」（有樣學樣）的「無腦行為」...。他呼籲新加坡人不要讓自己變得那麼「醜怪」（disgraceful）， 不能學別人那樣「低能」（idiot）。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad05b4560c6a1ac385874ac47fadc70a823c1f7f","tid":1976530,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"念眾生未"},{"pid":"c807ee0153f255bf22fbc5e7f51597c24ee0d296","tid":1976530,"uid":140253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"又冇食藥啦條友，口罩有足夠儲備，但係啲人全部有武漢肺炎，咁仲要口罩黎做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6354a4963fca1e9e64c7bc13bba57e486856062c","tid":1976530,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"條柒頭<br />\n撐咗篤屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72274841da42d4605b2d2697d6c94889b148648","tid":1976530,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"露底"},{"pid":"34cb0901b467626f5f10b1acd74857ab30c87cad","tid":1976530,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c807ee0153f255bf22fbc5e7f51597c24ee0d296","tid":1976530,"uid":140253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"又冇食藥啦條友，口罩有足夠儲備，但係啲人全部有武漢肺炎，咁仲要口罩黎做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"大部分人中曬有herd immunity咪以後唔駛搶口罩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d417264ccdf94ea7e1ca6d4e7bf29add122ff518","tid":1976530,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，死共狗"}]}